Dinotron crouched behind a tree as he watched Whistler come closer towards him. "Alright!" he thought,"I get to fight again!" 
DINOTRON MAXIMIZE!!!" He yelled. He transformed into robot mode and pulled out his sword. He charged towards Wistler swinging his sword.
